dc_description_s: Map of the Chinese province Ssŭ-ch'uan showing province boundaries, transportation, water features, telegraph lines, missions and populated places. Relief shown by spot heights. Eastern sheet "and" Western sheet." Includes a Chinese to English explanation and a list of Sources of information. "T.S.G.S. No. 2048." "Provisional issue without hills." Historic Maps copy imperfect: western sheet wanting.
dc_creator_sm: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Topographical Section
dc_publisher_s: Southampton : Reproduced and printed for the Topographical Section, General Staff, at the Ordnance Survey Office, 1906 [i.e. 1908]
